CBRE as the exclusive selling agent, is pleased to present 338 Mowbray Road, Chatswood. Presented in Sydney’s exclusive Lower North Shore as an opportunity to retain as a medical building, to convert into a house or undertake a residential lot subdivision (S.T.C.A). Offered with vacant possession after operating as Mowbray Family Practice for over 40 years. The property is a single storey full brick property on a significant land holding of 1,117sqm* with three (3) street frontages. 

338 Mowbray Road, Chatswood is located 7km* north of Sydney CBD on the prestigious Lower North Shore. The property benefits from its proximity to Chatswood CBD/Train & Metro Station with frequent services to Sydney CBD during peak hours, employment,  retail precincts, elite schools, and parks. 

338 Mowbray Road, Chatswood capitalises on the following key attributes:

•Operated as Mowbray Family Practice for over 40 years underwriting the strength of the premium location
•Significant land holding of 1,117sqm*
•Opportunity to retain as a medical practice, convert into a house, or undertake a residential lot subdivision (S.T.C.A)
•Desirable location 7km* north of Sydney CBD in proximity to Artarmon Train Station & shops, Chatswood Train/Metro Station, and Chatswood CBD, bus services, elite schools, and parks 
•Prominent corner block location with significant frontage to three (3) streets 
•650m* from council proposed Hampden Road Redevelopment (2036)
•Opportunity for childcare (STCA) 
•Five (5) General Practitioner consulting rooms
•Seven (7) car parking spaces at the rear of the property
•Robust property market with strong housing demand 

338 Mowbray Road, Chatswood will be sold via Public Auction on Tuesday 1 June, 2021 at AuctionWORKS - Mezzanine Level, 50 Margaret Street, Sydney (live stream & online bidding available).

For more information or to request access to the due diligence room, please contact the exclusive selling agents.

*Approx.

CBRE, under instructions from the Receivers & Managers, Peter Marsden and Richard Stone of RSM Australia Partners, are pleased to present Lot 6 & 8, 7 Help Street to market. The property is a large retail strata located in the highly popular suburb of Chatswood. Currently tenanted by the well-established Fook Yuen Seafood Restaurant, the yum cha venue is a prime offering to both investors and owner occupiers in a rapidly growing area.

Lot 6 & 8, 7 Help Street benefits from the following features:

- Tenanted by Fook Yuen Seafood Restaurant, a Cantonese yum cha venue with a long business history at the site
- Rent: $416,664 per annum* + GST
- 10 + 5 year lease (December 2011 lease commencement)
- Total strata area: 1,218sqm*
- 10 undercroft car spaces & a single lock up garage
- Strong Chinese demographic ideal for restaurant tenants
- Can be sold as leased or with vacant possession for owner occupiers

The property will be offered for sale by way of Expressions of Interest closing on Wednesday 8 November 2017 at 6:00PM AEST 

Note: All financial figures have been provided by the client. Purchasers are advised to conduct their own independent due diligence

For further details, please contact the exclusive CBRE selling agents.

*Approximate
